         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(Col. I: too fragmentary to be read);;(Col. II);;(Paid) to Sotas, workman, 20 drachmai 4 obols, and from the village from the 18th year till the 20th year 20 drachmai, total 103(?) drachmai of which for . . . 28 drachmai; and he worked in the reed-land of the estate on the mud wall from the 15th till Mesore 4th additional day.</ab>
